      "content": "it's just so hard to feel any \"peace\" when everything is so heavy. i feel like i'm just waiting for the inevitable anyway, just watching the clock tick down. sometimes i wonder if there's even any dignity in just letting it happen slowly like this... or if there's a better way to actually decide when it's over.",
